When Chris is not busy studying the [[Bible]], he likes to chat to young girls on [[MSN]]. It was therefore one of Chris' most perfect moments when he met [[16-year-old girl|13-year old]] "Jessica" on 10/14/07. Unfortunately, perfect is the enemy of good. Chris did not have the common sense to realize there are [[No_girls_on_the_internet|no girls on the internets]].  This, combined with a remarkable interest in [[CP|females of breeding age]], made him vulnerable to epic [[fail]].

When offered the virtual delicious loli, it did not take long for Chris to expose to the world his deepest desires and dreams. After seeing some pictures, he took an immediate interest in the little Jessica's [[Tits or GTFO|mammaries]] and [[Cunt|vagina]], inviting her to send her soiled panties to him, and as the kind Christian he is, offering her a place to stay.

Propositions like this would not be credible without some [[Webcam|camwork]]. After Chris had counted the seconds waiting for his church session to end, he was happy to find Jessica on MSN again and proceeded to [[Camwhore|whore it up]], at full force with his man-bits (''bits'' would be appropriate here, [[amirite]]?), mouth, and ass.

As expected, it turned out that Jessica's real name was [[Anonymous]]. Using the [[Pedo Baiting|subtle technique]] as popularized by [[Chris Hansen|people with seats]], the fine folks from [[ebaumsworld|ebaumsworld]] successfully trolled him.  They easily uncovered his [[docs|dox]] from the detailed information he provided, and proceeded to spam his praize.com blog and e-mail his church.

On '''Wednesday December 5th, 2007''' he was [[Party Horse]]d after the heroes at the [[Internet Vigilante Group]] sent out a [[Cyber Posse]] to help the [[bestiality|Royal Canadian Mounted Police]] round up this [[pedobear|menace to society]].

