*Jesus is [[Truth|Anonymous]].
*[[George Bush doesn't care about black people|Jesus doesn't give a shit about pedophiles.]]
*Jesus is [[X is not your personal army|not your personal army]].
*Chris was low on [[world of warcraft|mana]]
*Jesus was [[Pwned|pwned]] by Romans and Jew [[at least 100]] years ago.

Experts agree that Chris should have [[buy a dog|bought a dog]] instead, however, [[a cat is fine too]].

